    • getOwner

      @Nullable public com.mojang.datafixers.util.Either<BlockEntity,Entity> getOwner()
      Description copied from interface: IOwnedSpawner
      Returns the block entity or entity which owns this spawner object.

      For a BaseSpawner, this is the

      invalid reference 
      MobSpawnerBlockEntity
      or MinecartSpawner.

      For a TrialSpawner, this is the TrialSpawnerBlockEntity.
